titles.title: Search for chargino and neutralino production in final states with two same-sign leptons, jets and missing transverse momentum at $\sqrt{s}$ = 13 TeV with the ATLAS detector

record.abstract: This note serves as reference documentation on the ATLAS search for electroweakino pro- duction in final states with two same-sign leptons, missing transverse momentum and jets in 36.1 fb−1 of pp collisions at $\sqrt{s}$ = 13 TeV. R-parity conserving simplified supersymmetric scenarios are considered in which it is assumed that $\tilde{\chi}_{2}^{0}$ and $\tilde{\chi}_{1}^{\pm}$ decay respectively into h+ $\tilde{\chi}_{1}^{0}$ and into W ± + $\tilde{\chi}_{1}^{0}$ with BR=100%.
